# Google OAuth — get your Client ID from https://console.cloud.google.com
# 1. Create a project → APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# 2. Add http://localhost:5173 (and your production URL) to Authorized JavaScript origins
# 3. Copy the Client ID here
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com

